{"tid":1218444,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"中產同我入來！金融戰都要繼續","createTime":"2019-06-13T15:50:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T22:57:16.000Z","uid":241310,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ef10634e501235fc72eca535a688abefd3ecc392","tid":1218444,"uid":241310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:50:06.000Z","msg":"唔好再講咩香港大把錢，有錢佬都開始走，每人走啲每人走啲就好撚多<br />\n唔好再話咩連登無有錢人，尋日一個巴打獨力就拎咗一億！<br />\n雖然佢做錯咗，無正式「走資」，只係移離中資銀行<br />\n<br />\n咁到底點樣先可以正確走資？？？<br />\n走資唔止係為香港，同時都係為你自己、為屋企！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n／／／<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有巴打話我知在香港匯豐總行國際銀行業務部可以開英國户口 而不需要英國地址！各位中產朋友可以嘗試下！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://internationalservices.hsbc.com/zh-hk/index/account-opening\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finternationalservices.hsbc.com%2Fzh-hk%2Findex%2Faccount-opening&d=BIOOYiAB7dh8oRe%2BrusdWQfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=69f81598\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://internationalservices.hsbc.com/zh-hk/index/account-opening</a></span><br />\n／／／<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>馮敬恩：【金融戰第一步】究竟可以點樣走資？ TransferWise 簡介</strong></em><br />\n<a href=\"https://medium.com/@billyjaiishappy/%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D%E6%88%B0%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A5-%E7%A9%B6%E7%AB%9F%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E9%BB%9E%E6%A8%A3%E8%B5%B0%E8%B3%87-transferwise-%E7%B0%A1%E4%BB%8B-8cd30c0c7bd7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%40billyjaiishappy%2F%25E9%2587%2591%25E8%259E%258D%25E6%2588%25B0%25E7%25AC%25AC%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%25AD%25A5-%25E7%25A9%25B6%25E7%25AB%259F%25E5%258F%25AF%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E9%25BB%259E%25E6%25A8%25A3%25E8%25B5%25B0%25E8%25B3%2587-transferwise-%25E7%25B0%25A1%25E4%25BB%258B-8cd30c0c7bd7&d=BIOOYiAB7dh8oRe%2BrusdWQfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=b9e0b55c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://medium.com/@billyjaiishappy/%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D%E6%88%B0%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A5-%E7%A9%B6%E7%AB%9F%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E9%BB%9E%E6%A8%A3%E8%B5%B0%E8%B3%87-transferwise-%E7%B0%A1%E4%BB%8B-8cd30c0c7bd7</a>"},{"pid":"2821cf46bb172a683fc81331f1a83d0659dcd719","tid":1218444,"uid":241310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:06:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />走資喇喂"},{"pid":"831ef018d485029634f8b8d467c99d2b72962abf","tid":1218444,"uid":225916,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:11:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">千祈唔好</span>將走資消息整成廢老群祖啲訊息<br />\n有1個人做 就可能嚇到另一個走 就繼續有人會走<br />\n嚇到冇人敢接貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />然後直接谷底<br />\n<br />\n不過事實上今時今日....<br />\n資產價值真係值咁多咩???根本就係炒高咗好多<br />\n一跌就變到日本爆破咁"},{"pid":"d37fc88ed9094a78086062047c1b35f8f1e64aa7","tid":1218444,"uid":169074,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:14:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"426925e242aee8669dda577555c1a473d713a1d3","tid":1218444,"uid":241310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:22:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 走資喇喂"},{"pid":"8c025abad2d42390a2553c26a1bcf00a6c746f11","tid":1218444,"uid":241310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:25:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 走資喇喂"},{"pid":"b90c70d0c3e68db647c4027873d091fe6b4073bb","tid":1218444,"uid":50467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:38:08.000Z","msg":"大家幫推，呢個世界錢先係最重要"},{"pid":"82e9fcdc8a3c8c55ed557f4a4b3e665f974e795c","tid":1218444,"uid":241310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:55:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 走資喇喂"},{"pid":"8440c99428ee08d57306618e0d5919d03060a934","tid":1218444,"uid":92188,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T17:01:49.000Z","msg":"錢嘅威力最大，有錢嘅連登仔到你地發威"},{"pid":"b02